<p><span class="anchor" id="p46"></span>الْقيام على الْمَذْهَب إِن قدر<a href="#p46" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p47"></span>وَقيل يجوز الْقعُود مَعَ الْقُدْرَة<a href="#p47" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p48"></span>وَيسن رفع يَدَيْهِ فِي التَّكْبِيرَات<a href="#p48" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p49"></span>حَذْو مَنْكِبَيْه<a href="#p49" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
